everything that we know.

19:08.741 --> 19:10.281
Yeah,
but where do we start?

19:10.283 --> 19:12.906
Given me a headache
just thinking about it.

19:12.908 --> 19:14.573
We'll start with Caravaggio,

19:14.575 --> 19:17.031
then work our way back
to the ancients.

19:17.033 --> 19:18.239
Art, poetry, literature.

19:18.241 --> 19:20.406
There's a lot to learn
and we don't have much time.

19:20.408 --> 19:22.573
Yeah, but for now
we'll stick to the basics.

19:22.575 --> 19:24.739
To be honest,
that's the part of the job

19:24.741 --> 19:26.073
that worries me the most.

19:26.075 --> 19:27.364
I've had some trouble
in the past.

19:27.366 --> 19:31.531
