darker, more edgy.

22:17.533 --> 22:18.239
After a couple of drinks,

22:18.241 --> 22:21.573
I'd probably introduce him
to the Flagellation of Christ,

22:21.575 --> 22:22.614
painted in Naples, 1607.

22:22.616 --> 22:24.989
Caravaggio's on the run
after committing murder.

22:24.991 --> 22:27.406
He's tired, he's sick,
he's a bit paranoid.

22:27.408 --> 22:29.031
I like where you're going
with this.

22:29.033 --> 22:31.739
It's the perfect example
of his late period.

22:31.741 --> 22:32.489
The lighting is dramatic.

22:32.491 --> 22:34.906
Christ's tortured body
is lit in a singular spotlight.

22:34.908 --> 22:39.448
The other muscular figures
appear from deep, dark shadows.

22:39.450 --> 22:41.698
Good work.

22:41.700 --> 22:43.616
I'm impressed.

22:43.825 --> 22:45.489
Thanks.

22:45.491 --> 22:48.031
