- You've completely lost me.

23:50.491 --> 23:54.448
I'm just trying to figure out
which kind of things you prefer.

23:54.450 --> 23:55.489
Are you on drugs?

23:55.491 --> 23:58.406
I don't do drugs.
My body's a temple.

23:58.408 --> 23:59.781
Oh, I can see that.

23:59.783 --> 24:02.489
But, please, just try
and relax a little bit.

24:02.491 --> 24:03.406
You seem very tense.

24:03.408 --> 24:08.823
Sorry. You're my first client
and it's hard to relax in here.

24:08.825 --> 24:11.406
My mates tell me you're writing
a book on Caravaggio.

24:11.408 --> 24:15.739
Yes. And I saw that
you had an interest.

24:15.741 --> 24:19.698
But that's not the only reason
I invited you out, Jim.

24:19.700 --> 24:22.406
And please don't feel you need
to keep talking for my sake.

24:22.408 --> 24:28.573
I'm a Raconteur. Talking's
what I do. Amongst other things.

24:28.575 --> 24:32.656
I appreciate the irony,
I really do.

24:32.658 --> 24:36.033
But I saw your picture and...

24:36.950 --> 24:39.823
...you are probably one of
the most beautiful men

24:39.825 --> 24:41.864
I have ever seen.

24:41.866 --> 24:44.116
Thanks very much.

24:44.450 --> 24:45.448
