in the Vatican, apparently.

25:54.991 --> 25:56.906
The Entombment of Christ,

25:56.908 --> 25:59.323
painted by Caravaggio in 1601.

25:59.325 --> 26:02.698
Considered by many
to be the finest example of...

26:02.700 --> 26:06.823
