till I'm resurrected.

26:14.908 --> 26:17.031
The resurrection
will look after itself.

26:17.033 --> 26:18.948
Just tell me how
your first job went.

26:18.950 --> 26:22.698
The sex was great.
The problems came after.

26:22.700 --> 26:25.989
I think I'm too serious.
I need to lighten up.

26:25.991 --> 26:27.906
That's right. He does.

26:27.908 --> 26:29.781
I offered to pay him
but he was having none of it.

26:29.783 --> 26:35.325
That's not a great start, is it?
You think we do this for fun?

26:37.616 --> 26:39.573
Where's Caravaggio, by the way?

26:40.700 --> 26:42.073
Well, there's nobody out there.

26:42.075 --> 26:45.031
- Are you sure?
- Yeah, I'm sure.

26:45.033 --> 26:49.491
Maybe he's on the run.

27:03.366 --> 27:07.614
Was Caravaggio such a bad boy
or was half of it just made up?

27:07.616 --> 27:11.156
That's the beauty of it,
I suppose.

27:11.158 --> 27:13.325
We'll never really know.

27:13.908 --> 27:14.989
One part is true.

27:14.991 --> 27:18.989
We know he killed someone
in a duel.

27:18.991 --> 27:23.908
But parts of his life
are legend, I suspect.

27:25.825 --> 27:28.239
He's a fascinating character.

27:28.241 --> 27:30.156
And a great self-publicist.

27:30.158 --> 27:34.531
Just not the kind of man you
want to meet in a dark alley.

27:34.533 --> 27:39.241
That's exactly
where I'd like to meet him.

28:45.533 --> 28:48.448
You remind me
of someone I once knew.

28:51.700 --> 28:54.075
He's gone now.

28:57.950 --> 28:59.783
Do you miss him?

29:01.158 --> 29:03.241
I miss him terribly.

29:05.116 --> 29:06.948
He last wrote to me from Italy.

29:06.950 --> 29:10.698
He described a painting.
Beautiful.

29:10.700 --> 29:14.075
A painting that he saw
in a church.

29:14.491 --> 29:16.364
I never saw it.

29:16.366 --> 29:19.783
Except as a reproduction
in a book.

29:21.200 --> 29:24.033
I never saw him again either.

29:26.408 --> 29:29.239
Why so sad all of a sudden?

29:29.241 --> 29:33.158
I'm not sad.
Just thinking, is all.

29:36.116 --> 29:39.533
I wish you could see
that painting.

29:40.033 --> 29:42.989
I wish we could see it together.

29:42.991 --> 29:45.866
Don't be so serious.

29:50.241 --> 29:54.033
Enjoy your time
in the spotlight.

29:56.158 --> 29:58.700
I'll try.

30:24.158 --> 30:26.656
