this job any more.

30:26.658 --> 30:28.406
I think I'm too sensitive.

30:28.408 --> 30:28.906
It's early days.

30:28.908 --> 30:31.864
And part of what we do is listen
to other people's problems.

30:31.866 --> 30:32.906
It comes with the territory.

30:32.908 --> 30:35.864
But I take their problems
home with me at night.

30:35.866 --> 30:36.656
It's affecting my studies.

30:36.658 --> 30:39.531
Lie back and think of England.
This is what I do.

30:39.533 --> 30:40.823
Shouldn't you think of Spain?

30:40.825 --> 30:42.906
Try not to get
emotionally involved.

30:42.908 --> 30:43.906
I wanna be emotionally involved.

30:43.908 --> 30:46.448
I see a lot of loneliness
out there, a lot of sadness.

30:46.450 --> 30:49.948
This is London. Everyone's
lonely to a certain extent.

30:49.950 --> 30:52.698
That's why we need
to stick together.

30:55.033 --> 30:57.406
Hello?

30:57.408 --> 30:58.614
Yeah.

30:58.616 --> 30:59.781
Saint Sebastian?

30:59.783 --> 31:03.116
Painted by Guido Reni in 1625.

31:03.533 --> 31:07.366
Yeah, no worries.
Be there as soon as I can.

31:08.325 --> 31:08.823
