33:50.991 --> 33:54.614
in the privacy of a cheap hotel
room with a Catholic saint

33:54.616 --> 33:56.698
is my concern and not yours.

33:56.700 --> 33:59.448
Sorry.
I've done it again.

33:59.450 --> 34:00.906
I've spoilt the vibe.
You carry on.

34:00.908 --> 34:04.864
My dear boy, do you even know
the story of Saint Sebastian?

34:04.866 --> 34:07.323
I know he died a slow
and painful death

34:07.325 --> 34:08.364
at the hand of the Romans.

34:08.366 --> 34:10.072
And he was the world's first
male pin-up.

34:10.074 --> 34:13.489
Sebastian died
for the glory

34:13.491 --> 34:14.281
of our Lord Jesus Christ.

34:14.283 --> 34:18.072
